          "name": "Grille 3 cards avec icône",
          "desc": "3 colonnes, icône + titre + texte",
          "html": "<div class=\"row g-4\" style=\"margin:32px 0\">\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div style=\"background:var(--ws-gray-100);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;height:100%;transition:transform 0.2s\">\n      <div style=\"width:48px;height:48px;background:var(--bs-primary);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px\">\n        <span style=\"color:#fff;font-size:20px;font-weight:700\">1</span>\n      </div>\n      <h3 style=\"font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px\">Premier avantage</h3>\n      <p style=\"font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--ws-gray-600);margin:0;line-height:1.6\">Description courte de l'avantage. Chiffre concret si possible.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div style=\"background:var(--ws-gray-100);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;height:100%;transition:transform 0.2s\">\n      <div style=\"width:48px;height:48px;background:var(--ws-green-500);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px\">\n        <span style=\"color:#fff;font-size:20px;font-weight:700\">2</span>\n      </div>\n      <h3 style=\"font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px\">Deuxième avantage</h3>\n      <p style=\"font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--ws-gray-600);margin:0;line-height:1.6\">Description courte. Un fait vérifiable.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div style=\"background:var(--ws-gray-100);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;height:100%;transition:transform 0.2s\">\n      <div style=\"width:48px;height:48px;background:var(--ws-orange-500);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px\">\n        <span style=\"color:#fff;font-size:20px;font-weight:700\">3</span>\n      </div>\n      <h3 style=\"font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px\">Troisième avantage</h3>\n      <p style=\"font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--ws-gray-600);margin:0;line-height:1.6\">Description courte. Pas de superlatif, des faits.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
        },
        {
          "id": "grid-4-stats",
          "name": "Bande 4 chiffres clés",
          "desc": "4 stats en ligne, fond sombre",
          "html": "<div style=\"background:var(--ws-gray-900);border-radius:12px;padding:32px;margin:32px 0\">\n  <div class=\"row g-4 text-center\">\n    <div class=\"col-6 col-md-3\">\n      <div style=\"color:var(--bs-primary);font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1\">20+</div>\n      <div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:4px\">années d'expertise</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-6 col-md-3\">\n      <div style=\"color:var(--ws-green-400);font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1\">48h</div>\n      <div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:4px\">livraison standard</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-6 col-md-3\">\n      <div style=\"color:var(--ws-gold);font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1\">24h</div>\n      <div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:4px\">devis personnalisé</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-6 col-md-3\">\n      <div style=\"color:var(--ws-orange-400);font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1\">200€</div>\n      <div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:4px\">livraison offerte dès</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
        },
        {
          "id": "grid-2-image-text",
          "name": "2 colonnes image + texte",
          "desc": "Image à gauche, contenu à droite (ou inversé)",
          "html": "<div class=\"row g-4 align-items-center\" style=\"margin:32px 0\">\n  <div class=\"col-md-5\">\n    <img src=\"https://placehold.co/600x400/e9ecef/6c757d?text=Photo+produit\" alt=\"Description\" class=\"w-100\" style=\"border-radius:12px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-7\">\n    <h2 class=\"ws-h2\">Titre de la section</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;color:var(--ws-gray-700)\">Premier paragraphe. Mise en situation du lecteur dans son contexte professionnel. Vous + verbe d'action.</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;color:var(--ws-gray-700)\">Deuxième paragraphe. Donnée chiffrée, cas d'usage concret avec secteur nommé.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
        }
